text: Tommy Dorfman (born May 13, 1992) is an American actress and model. She is best known for playing Ryan Shaver in the Netflix series 13 Reasons Why (2017). Dorfman is queer. In November 2017, Dorfman came out as non-binary. On July 22, 2021, Dorfman came out as a transgender woman. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:1992 births Category:Transgender women Category:LGBT people from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Atlanta Category:LGBT models Category:Models from Georgia (U.S. state)
